SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4038
A bill to amend 2018 PA 175, entitled
"Insurance provider assessment act,"
by amending section 13 (MCL 550.1763).
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 13. (1) All money received and collected under this act
2 shall must be deposited by the department in the insurance provider
3 fund established in this section.
4 (2) The insurance provider fund is created within the state
5 treasury and shall must be administered by the department for
6 auditing purposes.
7 (3) The state treasurer may receive money or other assets from
8 any source for deposit into the fund. The state treasurer shall
9 direct the investment of the fund. The state treasurer shall credit
