1 PA 368, MCL 333.2508. Beginning January 1, 2029, and each January 1
2 after that date, the state treasurer shall adjust the amount under
3 this subdivision in accordance with the Consumer Price Index. As
4 used in this subdivision, "Consumer Price Index" means the annual
5 average percentage change in the Detroit Consumer Price Index for
6 all items for the prior 12-month period as reported by the United
7 States Department of Labor.
